[SN]TITLE[SN]
Serious two-vehicle crash closes A713

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A serious two-vehicle crash has closed the A713 at Drumjohn between Dalmellington in East Ayrshire and Dalry in Dumfries and Galloway.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police Scotland said emergency services had been called out to the accident at about 10:40.
They confirmed the incident was "still ongoing" but were unable to give details of any injuries.
Drivers were advised to try to avoid the area or expect delays.
